        • Mods: The server uses no mods<br>
        • Uptime: varies; usually %80 uptime<br>
        • Gamemode: Free-For-All (FFA)<br>
        • Maps: The map rotation currently consists of q2dm1 through q2dm8<br>
        • Maxplayers: currently the maxplayers is set to 8<br>
      </p>
      <p>
        Connecting to the server:<br>
        Open the console with the ` key and enter: connect ghostsquad57.com
      </p>
      <p>
